133131.name: Air Plant
133131.Description:
Air plants are interesting plants since they dont need 
soil to survive. These are great if youre looking 
for a small plant and dont want to deal with pots or soil. If you choose to house your air plant in a terrarium, make sure it has an opening so it gets plenty of circulation.
